						               													<description>We have combined GROM's expertise in everything related to the selection of raw materials, nature, food and the ingredients necessary to make the &amp;quot;best gelato in the world&amp;quot; with our creativity and experience in combining fun with educational content, and we have created the box that you have just opened.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Working together we have discovered that we have a common sensitivity towards the environment and people, attention to the little details that make the difference and we have put them in the box.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;I hope you have time, because the game... lasts one year! It lasts the four seasons to let you taste the best ingredients of each of them, represented by the tree in the middle of the board that you can dress and cover with its colorful flowers, leaves and snowflakes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A game lasts 4 rounds: one for each season.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In each season only those who complete a cup with at least three flavors of gelato earn points. To make a flavor you need the three basic ingredients and the ingredient of the flavor itself (eg. hazelnut or strawberry). The ingredients are won in the respective areas of the board and in the seasons in which they are available (e.g. fish at Mura Mura, but only in summer). The winner of the game is the one who, at the end of the fourth season, has scored the most points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
